Definition: a hypothetical object capable of absorbing all the electromagnetic radiation falling on it
Example: a black body maintained at a constant temperature is a full radiator at that temperature because the radiation reaching and leaving it must be in equilibrium
Synonyms: blackbody, full_radiator, noun, Tops, natural_object, a, hypothetical, object, capable, of, absorbing, all, the, electromagnetic, radiation, falling, on, it, black, body, maintained, at, constant, temperature, is, full, radiator, that, because, reaching, and, leaving, must, be, in, equilibrium
Category: noun.object
